        "subject": "LU-2335 build: add script to generate client code",
        "message": "LU-2335 build: add script to generate client code\n\nbuild/build-client-source.sh copies client only\ncode out and clean it up according to config.h.\n\nbuild/upstream-kbuild provides makefiles for kbuild.\n\nWith this commit, one can generate client kernel source\ncode and build via:\n1. ./configure\n2. sh build/build-client-source.sh\n3. cd lustre-client\n4. make\n\nSigned-off-by: Peng Tao <tao.peng@emc.com>\nChange-Id: I5ee55a63c49cd5d566f75ad6df32863977195e41\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
